nodes.text: Rebel Privateers! was a Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game adventure published in Star Wars Adventure Journal 2 written by Timothy S. O'Brien and illustrated by Douglas Shuler. It begins with a letter to Moff Gergris, Halthor Sector Command from Governor Thanis, Noonar. What follows is an article about privateers and their equipment. It was reprinted in The Best of the Star Wars Adventure Journal, Issues 1-4 in April 1996. The story was later published online at Hyperspace.
